OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,FSouth Western Ambulance Service has
OL,7,Fwarned it's facing "unprecedented
OL,8,Fdemand" and is urging people to only
OL,9,Fcall 999 in an emergency, after
OL,10,Fexperiencing its busiest day on record
OL,11,Flast month.
OL,13,FSoaring summer temperatures have put
OL,14,Fpressure on the service, and
OL,15,Fparamedics have told ITV News they're
OL,16,Fin danger of burnout responding to
OL,17,Fcalls that do not require an emergency
OL,18,Fresponse.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
