OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,FITV West Country joined crews in
OL,7,FSomerset and Cornwall on one of their
OL,8,Fshifts.
OL,10,FJust minutes into their 12-hour shift,
OL,11,FBridgwater-based paramedic Jess and
OL,12,Fcolleague Sam receive their first
OL,13,Femergency call: 53-year-old Duncan has
OL,14,Fan irregular heart rhythm and is
OL,15,Fstruggling to breathe.
OL,17,FClassed as category 2 - calls which
OL,18,Fare emergencies but not immediately
OL,19,Fcritical ` the crew soon arrives at
OL,20,Fhis home in Taunton.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,FAfter checking his heart rate, Jess
OL,7,Fand Sam decide he needs further
OL,8,Fchecks, and he is taken to Musgrove
OL,9,FHospital.
OL,11,FWhile they're trying to treat more
OL,12,Fpatients at home to reduce pressure on
OL,13,Fhospital services, Jess says there was
OL,14,Fno alternative but to bring him in.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,F"With his heart rate being so high,
OL,7,Fthey need to do manual interventions
OL,8,Fin order to try and bring it down,"
OL,9,Fshe says. "Whether or not that be
OL,10,Fthrough medications, or if worst comes
OL,11,Fto worst, sometimes they can use
OL,12,Felectrical intervention to try and get
OL,13,Fhis heart rate into a normal rhythm."
OL,15,FDuncan needed a controlled shock to
OL,16,Freset his heart rhythm before
OL,17,Freturning home.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,FAnother call takes Jess and Sam to an
OL,7,Fassisted living development, where an
OL,8,Felderly resident has suffered facial
OL,9,Finjuries after falling out of bed.
OL,11,FAfter checks, they decide 103-year-old
OL,12,FBarbara needs to be taken to hospital
OL,13,Ffor an X-ray, as osteoarthritis makes
OL,14,Fher more susceptible to broken bones.
OL,16,FOn break back in Bridgwater, Jess and
OL,17,FSam tell ITV West Country that the
OL,18,Fsustained demand is taking a
OL,19,Fsignificant toll on staff.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,FJess says: "I think there's an element
OL,7,Fof compassion fatigue, because
OL,8,Fobviously a lot of us didn't come into
OL,9,Fthe job for the money.
OL,11,F"Giving that compassion, a lot, to
OL,12,Fpeople sometimes who don't actually
OL,13,Fneed it can be quite testing at some
OL,14,Fpoints during your career. It can
OL,15,Fshorten people's careers because you
OL,16,Fend up with burnout."
OL,18,FSouth Western Ambulance Service is
OL,19,Fresponsible for ambulance provision
OL,20,Facross an area of 10,000 square miles,
OL,21,Fwhich is 20% of mainland England.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,FThe trust serves a total population of
OL,7,Fmore than 5.5 million people, and also
OL,8,Freceives an influx of around 23
OL,9,Fmillion visitors each year.
OL,11,FThe recent hot weather has triggered a
OL,12,Fsurge in 999 calls, with paramedics
OL,13,Fbeing sent out to thousands more
OL,14,Fincidents.
OL,16,FDuring the June heatwave, the South
OL,17,FWestern Ambulance Service said it
OL,18,Fresponded to its busiest day on record.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,FOn Thursday 25 June, the trust
OL,7,Freceived more than 5,200 calls to its
OL,8,F999 control room and managed more than
OL,9,F4,300 incidents across the region -
OL,10,Fthe highest level of demand ever
OL,11,Frecorded by the service.
OL,13,FFurther south in Newquay, Christian
OL,14,Fand Harvey start their shift with a
OL,15,Fcategory 2 call from an 83-year-old
OL,16,Fman with chest pain.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,FAfter setting up an ECG
OL,7,F(electrocardiogram) to monitor Geoff's
OL,8,Fheart, Harvey the paramedic decides he
OL,9,Fneeds to be taken to hospital for
OL,10,Ffurther treatment.
OL,12,FHowever, when they arrive, they find
OL,13,Ftheir patient could be waiting hours
OL,14,Ffor a hospital bed to become available.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,F"It's quite a busy day, so all the
OL,7,Fambulances are holding," Christian
OL,8,Fsays. "So our patient is going in for
OL,9,Fa triage. He's going in to have his
OL,10,Fbloods done, and then, because it's so
OL,11,Fbusy, he's going to come back and wait
OL,12,Fin the ambulance for the results to be
OL,13,Fprocessed.
OL,15,F"Today is one of those particular days
OL,16,Fwhere it's insanely busy. So, I think
OL,17,Fthere are at least 14 ambulances here,
OL,18,Fso we could be here for quite a few
OL,19,Fhours, unfortunately."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,F"We've got a little bit used to it,"
OL,7,FChristian continues. "It's quite
OL,8,Ffrustrating as a front-line worker, as
OL,9,Fnaturally, you want to be out helping."
OL,11,FOnce the crew becomes available again,
OL,12,Fthe next call swiftly follows. A man
OL,13,Fhas got into trouble swimming at
OL,14,FCarlyon Bay.
OL,16,FAfter checks, Christian and Harvey
OL,17,Fconfirm he has had a "lucky escape"
OL,18,Fand doesn't need to be taken to
OL,19,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,F"Looking at your observations, all
OL,7,Fyour numbers are looking okay," Harvey
OL,8,Fsays. "Your chest sounds clear. You've
OL,9,Fnot got any frothing around the mouth.
OL,10,FI think you've had a lucky escape."
OL,12,FHarvey says that many of the incidents
OL,13,Fthey attend could be prevented.
OL,15,F"Over 50% of patients we leave at
OL,16,Fhome, which probably goes to show that
OL,17,Fthey're not life-threatening
OL,18,Femergencies.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,F"They're trying their best to deal
OL,7,Fwith things on the phone, and they're
OL,8,Ftrying their best to deal with things
OL,9,Fbefore it even comes to us, to limit
OL,10,Fthe ambulance use."
OL,12,FAnalysis by Richard Payne
OL,14,FWe can all probably agree that it
OL,15,Ftakes a certain type of person to be
OL,16,Fan emergency ambulance worker.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,FSeeing the public at their worst -
OL,7,Fencountering incidents that some
OL,8,Fpeople don't survive - requires a
OL,9,Fresolve most of us don't possess. Add
OL,10,Fin stretched resources and long,
OL,11,Fstressful hours for less money than
OL,12,Fyou might earn at Amazon, and you
OL,13,Fwonder why they do it.
OL,15,FHaving spent the day with them, I'm
OL,16,Fjust grateful they do.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,FFrom 6.30am to 8pm, the two crew
OL,7,Fmembers who shared their working world
OL,8,Fwith us were constantly on the move.
OL,9,FNot, thankfully, to fatal incidents
OL,10,Finvolving multiple casualties, but the
OL,11,Feveryday ones you'd want handled with
OL,12,Fspeed, care, and skill if it was you
OL,13,For your loved one on the receiving end.
OL,15,FI've been lucky enough to witness
OL,16,F'behind the scenes' of the emergency
OL,17,Fservices many times, and their ability
OL,18,Fto cope when often everyone around
OL,19,Fthem is doing anything but, always
OL,20,Fleaves a lasting impression.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,FIt was no different as we bounced from
OL,7,Fone job to the next: the husband and
OL,8,Ffather struggling with a racing heart,
OL,9,Fthe remarkable 103-year-old who'd
OL,10,Ffallen out of bed, and the cancer
OL,11,Fpatient needing care and advice.
OL,13,FTime and again, ambulance crews show
OL,14,Fup, even when they shouldn't. Time-
OL,15,Fwasting calls come too often from
OL,16,Fpeople who can't get through to the GP
OL,17,For, amazingly, see an ambulance as a
OL,18,Flift to the hospital, thinking it will
OL,19,Fjump them up the queue.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1784659707
OL,3,CSouth Western Ambulance Service facing
OL,4,C'unprecedented demand'
OL,6,FSpending half an hour in the back of
OL,7,Fan ambulance, weaving through the
OL,8,FSomerset countryside at speeds of up
OL,9,Fto 70mph and in soaring temperatures,
OL,10,Fis not an experience I'd ever want to
OL,11,Frepeat. Paramedics do it daily, of
OL,12,Fcourse, alongside patients who are
OL,13,Foften placing their lives in the hands
OL,14,Fof the professionals.
OL,16,FNearly 14 hours on the road made me
OL,17,Fgrateful for the end of the shift,
OL,18,Fespecially knowing that, unlike our
OL,19,Fambulance crews, I wouldn't be doing
OL,20,Fit all again the very next day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/18
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
